  dialogueHidesSubmit: 0
  lines:
  - "All my family went through on the first day\u2026. So why have I had to wait
    until now?"
  - "I hope they\u2019re ok\u2026 I mean, what if they were just more at risk?"
  - "Yeah, that\u2019s probably it, right? They just prioritized anyone at greater
    risk, yeah, that makes sense."
